title: 11/03/20 DPS-BEST OF
itunes:title: 11/03/20 DPS-BEST OF
description:
On Today's episode of the Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Giants/Bucs matchup. Is Daniel Jones the answer for the Giants going forward? Today's the NFL Trade deadline, will we see JJ Watt get moved? We're joined by Former NFL Head Coach Tony Dungy, Saints' pass rusher Cam Jordan and NFL Network Host, Rich Eisen. Plus, DP shares his experience voting this morning.
